  "title": "체형교정추나요법&lt;이수역사당남성역이수한의원&gt;",
  "addDate": "2013. 1. 24.",
  "categoryNo": "13",
  "parentCategoryNo": "7",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110157705123",
  "html_size": 181371,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110157705123\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110157705123\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff; COLOR: #000000\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff; COLOR: #000000\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff; COLOR: #000000\"></span><strong><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff; COLOR: #ff0000\">허리통증의 원인은 무엇이 있을까</span></strong><span style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff; COLOR: #ff0000\">?</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>청소년, 직장인들 장시간동안 의자에 오래앉아 컴퓨터나 책을 볼때 바르지 못한 자세로 있을때</p>\r\n<p>허리 통증을 호소하는 경우가 많다</p>\r\n<p>특히 의자 앉을때 구부리거나 턱을 괴는 자세를 오랫동안 유지를 하면 척추 측만증으로 이어질수있다</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1e8e4d7b3a22bc53.png\" width=\"493\" height=\"311\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 493px; rheight: 311px\" id=\"20130124_295/isuhani_1359013809846uqzPC_PNG/%C0%DA%BC%BC.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5E92FA3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1e8e4d7b3a22bc53.png\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>척추 측만증이란</strong>,<u> 눈으로 봤을때 양어깨의 높이가 다르고 등뒤에서 보기에 척추가 휘어져 있거나 </u></p>\r\n<p><u>견갑골이 튀어나와 있는증상을 말한다</u></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0000\">추나요법 치료 대상자는 ?</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>목디스크, 허리디스크, 좌골신경통, 만성요통 ,짝다리등의 효과적으로 나타나고</p>\r\n<p>성장기 아이들은 체형교정으로 키크는데에 도움이되고 자세교정도 된다</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fcf01069649a181d.png\" width=\"198\" height=\"131\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 198px; rheight: 131px\" id=\"20130124_40/isuhani_135901489171488QVO_PNG/%C0%DA%BC%BC2.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5E92FA3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fcf01069649a181d.png\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\"></span></strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\">허리통증</span><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\"> 예방하기</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>책상걸상은 본인키에 맞추기</p>\r\n<p>장시간 의자에 앉을땐 바른자세 스트레칭 하기</p>\r\n<p>서있을때 짝다리 하지않기</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130124_117/isuhani_1358997723868F3nqK_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"193\" height=\"48\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 193px; rheight: 48px\" id=\"20130124_117/isuhani_1358997723868F3nqK_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5E92FA3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130124_117/isuhani_1358997723868F3nqK_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
